{"tid":1816811,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JYP娛樂對TWICE娜璉跟蹤狂進行了刑事起訴","createTime":"2020-01-08T14:17:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T02:26:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb3b7c1d7349031f01a370ee096dac941e397bb0","tid":1816811,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"bnt新聞訊韓國人氣組合TWICE所屬社JYP娛樂對成員娜璉的跟蹤狂進行了刑事起訴。<br />\n<br />\n8日，JYP娛樂公司向首爾江南警察署以妨礙公務罪，刑事告發了娜璉的外籍跟蹤狂。<br />\n<br />\n而此前7日已經向首爾中央地方法院提交了禁止接近的假處分申請。<br />\n<br />\nJYP娛樂方面表示：&ldquo;我司已經在警察在場的情況下，對試圖持續接近娜璉的跟蹤狂表示絕對不能接近的警告&rdquo;，但跟蹤狂卻置之不理，甚至在1日的回程飛機上再次試圖接近，引起巨大騷動，因此決定進行起訴。<br />\n<br />\n另外，TWICE娜璉從上月初開始受到了跟蹤威脅，該外籍跟蹤狂曾通過SNS多次聲稱自己正在與娜璉交往。"},{"pid":"7fbe9d10c598194f73977d13b18c375ada1279ac","tid":1816811,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/ConcreteMixedBlackfish.webp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FConcreteMixedBlackfish.webp&h=1d40d7fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84d452cf0a430f188458ee6d69de3c43d2924923","tid":1816811,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/16e04bdff2516942fe6067b1eb47a340/a308ac63efdc0923-0f/s400x600/ba913dd1288c5974854f8f132c45bb55f2c8d951.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F16e04bdff2516942fe6067b1eb47a340%2Fa308ac63efdc0923-0f%2Fs400x600%2Fba913dd1288c5974854f8f132c45bb55f2c8d951.gifv&h=a061a9e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/6cda54f7618521fee9b4e275312ad681/a308ac63efdc0923-8f/s400x600/15d28a6d2671e893c730b62d967936c98199c81b.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F6cda54f7618521fee9b4e275312ad681%2Fa308ac63efdc0923-8f%2Fs400x600%2F15d28a6d2671e893c730b62d967936c98199c81b.gifv&h=e04c2902&s={SIZE}\" 